            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the<strong> tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Wash the <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>tomato wedges </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1607345467042-x200.jpg",
